The new Lithuanian comedy “Liars” produced by Paulius Virbickas, the producer of the Lithuanian movie hits “Inexperienced” and “Speaking among us, boys...”, and by producers Stasys Baltakis and Vladimiras Razarionovas, gets the viewers involved into comic and intriguing family peripeteias already from the first minutes of the movie.
