Tragic fate of a couple: died just few hours after getting married
The newlyweds, who got married just few hours ago, died in a helicopter crash in the southwest Texas, the USA.
William Troy Byler and his wife Bailee Raye Ackerman Byler, both 24, died on Sunday soon after midnight after the helicopter crashed into a hill 16 km northwest of Uvalde and 129 kilometers west of San Antonio, said Steven Kennedy, local justice of the peace.
